00:29:08,300 --> 00:29:10,300
Why are you looking for your father?

588
00:29:13,620 --> 00:29:14,440
Prepare some white noodles and eggs

589
00:29:14,440 --> 00:29:15,800
for Zhang.

590
00:29:16,460 --> 00:29:18,540
If we don't have enough money,

591
00:29:19,170 --> 00:29:20,150
pick some of

592
00:29:20,300 --> 00:29:21,500
Xiu'er and your jewelry

593
00:29:21,500 --> 00:29:22,300
and pawn them.

594
00:29:30,360 --> 00:29:31,010
I'm so mad.

595
00:30:08,090 --> 00:30:09,350
Why are you still here?

596
00:30:10,950 --> 00:30:11,900
I thought

597
00:30:11,900 --> 00:30:12,710
you would go back

598
00:30:12,710 --> 00:30:14,140
after you sent Youheng off.

599
00:30:14,140 --> 00:30:15,540
Did you stay up all night?

600
00:30:24,060 --> 00:30:25,060
I couldn't sleep.

601
00:30:26,390 --> 00:30:28,520
Something major happened to my family

602
00:30:29,540 --> 00:30:30,760
and Seven is still young

603
00:30:30,760 --> 00:30:32,620
so someone has to take care of him.

604
00:30:34,540 --> 00:30:35,270
And my father

605
00:30:35,700 --> 00:30:36,500
is always

606
00:30:36,660 --> 00:30:38,320
being controlled by Grandma.

607
00:30:40,220 --> 00:30:41,180
It's really one worrying thing

608
00:30:41,180 --> 00:30:42,310
after another.

609
00:30:44,940 --> 00:30:45,660
Then why are you wasting your time

610
00:30:45,660 --> 00:30:46,900
lamenting here?

611
00:30:48,870 --> 00:30:50,260
Have you fed the chickens?

612
00:30:50,260 --> 00:30:51,750
Have you washed the dishes?

613
00:30:51,750 --> 00:30:52,860
You promised to help me earn 200 taels of silver

614
00:30:52,860 --> 00:30:54,310
to save my hometown friend.

615
00:30:54,310 --> 00:30:55,770
Have you earned the money?

616
00:30:56,500 --> 00:30:57,560
This is not the time

617
00:30:57,690 --> 00:30:59,020
to talk to me about that.

618
00:31:16,470 --> 00:31:16,910
Ye'er?

619
00:31:17,080 --> 00:31:18,010
Why are you here?

620
00:31:22,230 --> 00:31:23,910
How is Aunt Zhang?

621
00:31:25,780 --> 00:31:27,180
Don't worry. She's fine.

622
00:31:29,500 --> 00:31:30,260
That's good.

623
00:31:31,030 --> 00:31:31,870
That's good.

624
00:31:33,030 --> 00:31:33,660
Ye'er.

625
00:31:35,630 --> 00:31:37,230
Do you have something to say?

626
00:31:39,270 --> 00:31:41,220
No, I don't.

627
00:31:49,140 --> 00:31:49,710
Is your mother

628
00:31:49,710 --> 00:31:50,910
