629
00:31:50,910 --> 00:31:51,710
Of course not.

630
00:31:56,410 --> 00:31:57,980
I know what you're thinking.

631
00:31:57,980 --> 00:31:59,710
But before Mother fell asleep just now,

632
00:31:59,710 --> 00:32:00,840
I already asked her.

633
00:32:01,660 --> 00:32:02,140
She said

