635
00:32:03,380 --> 00:32:04,290
by herself.

636
00:32:07,310 --> 00:32:08,870
Something is out of the ordinary.

637
00:32:08,870 --> 00:32:10,130
Something must be off.

638
00:32:20,930 --> 00:32:22,460
Are you going to the fields?

639
00:32:22,980 --> 00:32:23,800
Be careful.

640
00:32:24,030 --> 00:32:24,460
Okay.

641
00:32:47,900 --> 00:32:49,900
Aunt Zhang, what's wrong?

642
00:32:50,710 --> 00:32:51,700
How did you fall?

643
00:32:52,540 --> 00:32:53,660
What hit you?

644
00:33:34,810 --> 00:33:36,140
Youheng, you're smart.

645
00:33:37,060 --> 00:33:37,990
Why are you here?

646
00:33:55,940 --> 00:33:57,670
When I was treating Aunt Zhang,

647
00:33:58,230 --> 00:33:59,410
I accidentally found some scratches

648
00:33:59,410 --> 00:34:00,610
on her belly.

649
00:34:01,110 --> 00:34:01,740
It looks like they were left behind

650
00:34:01,740 --> 00:34:03,470
after hitting something hard.

651
00:34:03,990 --> 00:34:05,780
But I heard from Man'er's father that

652
00:34:05,780 --> 00:34:06,380
Aunt Zhang

653
00:34:06,590 --> 00:34:07,900
did fall in the fields.

654
00:34:09,139 --> 00:34:11,469
When the farmers cultivate their fields,

655
00:34:11,469 --> 00:34:12,520
they would never leave behind

656
00:34:12,520 --> 00:34:13,719
such an obvious rock.

657
00:34:16,010 --> 00:34:16,909
Maybe someone

658
00:34:17,750 --> 00:34:18,780
did it on purpose?

659
00:34:21,380 --> 00:34:22,980
I was suspicious last night,

660
00:34:23,060 --> 00:34:25,389
but I didn't dare to make any assumptions.

661
00:34:25,690 --> 00:34:27,290
Right now, seeing this rope,

662
00:34:27,389 --> 00:34:28,989
I could guess the situation.

663
00:34:29,770 --> 00:34:30,460
This rope

664
00:34:31,130 --> 00:34:32,480
must have been used by the assailant

665
00:34:32,480 --> 00:34:33,780
to trip Aunt Zhang

666
00:34:34,260 --> 00:34:35,520
