667
00:34:36,469 --> 00:34:37,060
Youheng.

668
00:34:38,020 --> 00:34:39,110
It's a pity that you're not going to the government

669
00:34:39,110 --> 00:34:39,969
to solve cases.

670
00:34:42,540 --> 00:34:43,400
What about you?

671
00:34:44,300 --> 00:34:46,239
You didn't see Aunt Zhang's injury.

672
00:34:46,239 --> 00:34:47,170
Why are you here?

673
00:34:49,300 --> 00:34:51,030
Although I didn't see the injury,

674
00:34:51,030 --> 00:34:52,540
judging from people's intentions,

675
00:34:52,540 --> 00:34:53,870
I could see the details.

676
00:34:55,210 --> 00:34:56,110
A few days ago,

677
00:34:56,550 --> 00:34:57,080
Mr. Lian

678
00:34:57,100 --> 00:34:58,170
wanted his eldest son

679
00:34:58,170 --> 00:34:59,430
to adopt Aunt's child.

680
00:34:59,790 --> 00:35:01,320
As soon as it was mentioned,

681
00:35:01,360 --> 00:35:03,160
Aunt fell and had a miscarriage.

682
00:35:03,550 --> 00:35:05,950
There is no such coincidence in this world.

683
00:35:06,760 --> 00:35:07,600
Even though the Lian family

684
00:35:07,600 --> 00:35:09,800
seem to be affectionate on the surface,

685
00:35:10,560 --> 00:35:12,620
they each have their own intentions.

686
00:35:13,380 --> 00:35:15,040
This time, I'm here to find out

687
00:35:15,580 --> 00:35:16,590
who did it.

688
00:35:18,920 --> 00:35:19,450
You already know

689
00:35:19,450 --> 00:35:20,460
who did it.

690
00:35:23,020 --> 00:35:24,880
This rope is not enough evidence.

691
00:35:25,390 --> 00:35:26,320
There is someone

692
00:35:27,220 --> 00:35:28,820
who can confirm my thoughts.

693
00:35:51,570 --> 00:35:52,140
Ye'er.

694
00:35:54,990 --> 00:35:55,540
Man'er.

695
00:35:56,260 --> 00:35:56,910
Sit down.

696
00:35:57,180 --> 00:35:57,870
Come, sit.

697
00:35:59,870 --> 00:36:00,710
Every day,

698
00:36:00,980 --> 00:36:02,730
we only eat millet and steamed bun.

699
00:36:02,730 --> 00:36:04,300
I don't have a drop of oil in my stomach.

700
00:36:04,300 --> 00:36:05,730
You also want to eat something good too, right?

701
00:36:05,730 --> 00:36:06,090
Here.

702
00:36:06,610 --> 00:36:07,030
This

703
00:36:07,070 --> 00:36:08,330
is the egg I just fried.

704
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:10,890
Isn't this egg from Grandpa

705
00:36:11,050 --> 00:36:12,470
for your mother?

706
00:36:12,870 --> 00:36:14,200
How can you give it to me?

707
00:36:14,620 --> 00:36:16,320
This is from my mother.

708
00:36:16,340 --> 00:36:17,270
It's not from me.

709
00:36:17,910 --> 00:36:18,460
She said

710
00:36:18,590 --> 00:36:20,270
that in our family, you work the most

711
00:36:20,270 --> 00:36:21,210
and are the most exhausted.

712
00:36:21,210 --> 00:36:23,210
She told me that I must give it to you.

713
00:36:28,570 --> 00:36:29,590
Eat up.

714
00:36:30,200 --> 00:36:31,460
Later, when Grandma and the others come to the kitchen

715
00:36:31,460 --> 00:36:32,660
to cook and notice it,

716
00:36:32,930 --> 00:36:34,390
you won't be able to eat it.

717
00:36:42,980 --> 00:36:43,840
I didn't expect

718
00:36:44,110 --> 00:36:45,910
my mother to care for you so much.

719
00:36:47,160 --> 00:36:47,640
It seems

720
00:36:47,960 --> 00:36:49,510
that you're just distant on the surface,

721
00:36:49,510 --> 00:36:50,250
but in private,

722
00:36:50,250 --> 00:36:51,710
you're very close, right?

723
00:36:53,210 --> 00:36:54,070
You have no idea

724
00:36:54,110 --> 00:36:55,520
that when my mother gave birth to me

725
00:36:55,520 --> 00:36:57,120
and found out that I was a girl.

726
00:36:57,120 --> 00:36:58,180
she didn't like me.

727
00:36:58,670 --> 00:37:00,100
My father didn't like me either.

728
00:37:00,100 --> 00:37:00,790
So he sent me

729
00:37:00,830 --> 00:37:01,970
to Aunt Zhang.

730
00:37:02,430 --> 00:37:02,950
When I was young,

731
00:37:02,950 --> 00:37:04,150
Aunt Zhang raised me.

732
00:37:04,550 --> 00:37:06,010
You were not born yet then.

733
00:37:16,150 --> 00:37:17,930
Aunt Zhang adored kids a lot.

734
00:37:19,050 --> 00:37:20,560
But she lost

735
00:37:21,020 --> 00:37:21,860
her own child.

736
00:37:23,100 --> 00:37:24,950
Aunt Zhang must be very sad.

737
00:37:28,520 --> 00:37:29,110
Yes.

738
00:37:31,420 --> 00:37:32,300
All day,

739
00:37:33,020 --> 00:37:34,480
she's just in a daze in bed.

740
00:37:35,060 --> 00:37:36,660
Her daze lasts an entire day.

741
00:37:38,350 --> 00:37:40,150
She kept reciting Eight's name.

742
00:37:43,670 --> 00:37:45,030
My mother's physical injuries

743
00:37:45,030 --> 00:37:46,430
are recovering quickly.

744
00:37:46,760 --> 00:37:47,640
But I don't know

745
00:37:49,590 --> 00:37:52,390
how long it'll take for her emotional pain to heal.

746
00:37:56,500 --> 00:37:57,410
Besides,

747
00:37:59,820 --> 00:38:01,880
her miscarriage wasn't an accident.

748
00:38:08,730 --> 00:38:09,420
Right?

749
00:38:15,640 --> 00:38:16,480
I don't know.

750
00:38:17,430 --> 00:38:17,990
Ye'er.

751
00:38:20,200 --> 00:38:21,330
You know about this?

752
00:38:23,410 --> 00:38:23,860
I...

753
00:38:24,110 --> 00:38:25,710
Man'er, I really don't know.

754
00:38:28,250 --> 00:38:30,310
You said my mother was the best to you.

755
00:38:30,660 --> 00:38:31,440
She thought

756
00:38:31,460 --> 00:38:33,190
her miscarriage was her fault.

757
00:38:33,580 --> 00:38:34,380
Every day, she can't eat

758
00:38:34,380 --> 00:38:35,100
nor sleep.

759
00:38:35,790 --> 00:38:37,430
Why won't you tell the truth?

760
00:38:37,970 --> 00:38:38,710
Why can't you

761
00:38:38,750 --> 00:38:40,280
make my mother feel better?

762
00:38:40,490 --> 00:38:41,150
It's not me.

763
00:38:41,310 --> 00:38:42,640
It's not that I don't want to tell you,

764
00:38:42,640 --> 00:38:43,790
but that I can't.

765
00:38:43,810 --> 00:38:44,950
Why not?

766
00:38:46,170 --> 00:38:47,770
Is someone threatening you?

767
00:38:47,950 --> 00:38:48,980
Don't force me.

768
00:38:48,980 --> 00:38:49,780
You can't tell

769
00:38:51,190 --> 00:38:52,720
because this rope is yours.

770
00:38:58,860 --> 00:38:59,340
Man'er.

771
00:39:00,450 --> 00:39:01,350
This rope

772
00:39:02,070 --> 00:39:02,620
was found

773
00:39:02,660 --> 00:39:04,790
at the area where your mother tripped.

774
00:39:04,820 --> 00:39:05,940
Your mother was tripped

775
00:39:05,940 --> 00:39:06,670
by this rope.

776
00:39:11,820 --> 00:39:12,430
Isn't this

777
00:39:12,470 --> 00:39:13,750
the rope you often use?

778
00:39:16,140 --> 00:39:17,150
In our household, you're the only one

779
00:39:17,150 --> 00:39:19,410
who goes up the mountain to get firewood.

780
00:39:20,030 --> 00:39:20,620
Man'er.

781
00:39:21,460 --> 00:39:22,380
The rope is mine.

782
00:39:22,380 --> 00:39:23,710
But it really wasn't me.

783
00:39:24,800 --> 00:39:26,060
I didn't say you did it.

784
00:39:26,860 --> 00:39:27,470
The person who did it

785
00:39:27,470 --> 00:39:28,500
is not smart.

786
00:39:29,320 --> 00:39:31,380
When they tripped Aunt on the fields,

787
00:39:31,670 --> 00:39:33,140
they used too much strength

788
00:39:33,140 --> 00:39:34,270
and hurt their hand.

789
00:39:35,280 --> 00:39:36,680
That's why there is blood

790
00:39:36,710 --> 00:39:37,970
on one side of the rope.

791
00:39:38,500 --> 00:39:39,530
But look at Ye'er.

792
00:39:40,030 --> 00:39:41,630
There is no wound on her hand.

793
00:39:41,820 --> 00:39:42,420
Someone must have

794
00:39:42,420 --> 00:39:43,750
took the rope on purpose

795
00:39:44,060 --> 00:39:45,590
so that they could frame her

796
00:39:45,910 --> 00:39:47,370
when things come to light.

797
00:39:54,550 --> 00:39:56,210
Right now, in the Lian family,

798
00:39:56,270 --> 00:39:57,930
whoever has a wound on the hand

799
00:39:58,180 --> 00:39:59,040
is the culprit.

800
00:40:03,980 --> 00:40:05,580
It should be easy to find out.

801
00:40:12,070 --> 00:40:12,890
When Aunt fell that dy,

802
00:40:12,890 --> 00:40:14,890
