803
00:40:14,940 --> 00:40:16,460
So when you came over that day,

804
00:40:16,460 --> 00:40:16,980
you were hesitant about

805
00:40:16,980 --> 00:40:18,780
whether to tell the truth or not.

806
00:40:20,870 --> 00:40:22,260
Should I say her name

807
00:40:23,540 --> 00:40:24,740
or do you want to do it?

808
00:40:35,410 --> 00:40:36,020
What?

809
00:40:39,420 --> 00:40:40,620
These days,

810
00:40:40,660 --> 00:40:41,980
you've been lying in bed

811
00:40:41,980 --> 00:40:44,020
