812
00:40:44,020 --> 00:40:45,550
Such a big thing happened in this family

813
00:40:45,550 --> 00:40:46,210
because...

814
00:40:49,820 --> 00:40:50,820
That's not right.

815
00:40:51,810 --> 00:40:53,160
I know how capable

816
00:40:53,180 --> 00:40:54,590
my daughter is.

817
00:40:55,390 --> 00:40:56,390
You wouldn't dare

818
00:40:56,420 --> 00:40:58,180
to do such a thing.

819
00:40:58,660 --> 00:40:59,190
Right?

820
00:40:59,190 --> 00:41:00,990
Is Lian Hua'er messing with you?

821
00:41:02,550 --> 00:41:04,380
I didn't say anything.

822
00:41:05,300 --> 00:41:06,650
You said it yourself.

823
00:41:06,830 --> 00:41:07,610
At this time,

824
00:41:07,630 --> 00:41:09,100
