825
00:41:09,100 --> 00:41:09,820
You're just like your mother.

826
00:41:09,820 --> 00:41:11,280
You have a one-track mind.

827
00:41:11,880 --> 00:41:12,950
Lian Hua'er,

828
00:41:12,990 --> 00:41:14,460
that wrench,

829
00:41:14,630 --> 00:41:16,670
