830
00:41:16,670 --> 00:41:17,950
It's all Lian Man'er's fault.

831
00:41:17,950 --> 00:41:19,780
She bullies me all the time.

832
00:41:20,360 --> 00:41:22,020
Hua'er just wanted to help me,

833
00:41:22,060 --> 00:41:24,670
so she asked me along to mess with Zhang.

834
00:41:25,740 --> 00:41:27,040
So that Lian Man'er

835
00:41:27,060 --> 00:41:28,260
would be infuriated.

836
00:41:28,980 --> 00:41:29,860
But who knew

837
00:41:30,430 --> 00:41:31,600
that a trip

838
00:41:31,860 --> 00:41:33,960
would result in such a severe fall.

839
00:41:33,980 --> 00:41:35,430
You dim-witted girl.

840
00:41:35,470 --> 00:41:37,740
Lian Hua'er is just using you as a scapegoat.

841
00:41:37,740 --> 00:41:39,900
What good intention can she have?

842
00:41:40,050 --> 00:41:42,090
Then what should I do now?

843
00:41:42,460 --> 00:41:45,150
If Shouxin and Father find out,

844
00:41:45,620 --> 00:41:48,160
