845
00:41:48,180 --> 00:41:49,060
Stop crying.

846
00:41:50,260 --> 00:41:51,660
What's the use of crying?

847
00:41:55,090 --> 00:41:56,750
She's really

848
00:41:57,670 --> 00:41:58,830
cunning.

849
00:42:00,170 --> 00:42:02,400
You must be careful of Lian Hua'er.
